replies.body:
If you're actually looking for tips to improve, I have a few from the limited points I saw in the video

Your cs was extremely low. Sure, you had a lead because you were kills up, but if you had more CS as well you would've been much stronger.

@2:14- Your wave was slow pushing into the enemy top laner. You should not have tried to take a fight there, because most junglers will know that you will soon be overextended and look to gank that.

You wound up getting a huge lead, but instead of roaming and helping your team get ahead as well, you sat top lane, even when you were losing inhibs. 

@11- You went mid and went for the win despite your yasuo going bot. 

And these are just things I picked up from your highlights. I imagine if  I saw the full vod there would be much more.
